reviewText: Gave as a present.  Well received.

Excellent documentary on the engineering trials, tribulations and pure genius that went in to the development of the latest generation of Harley-Davidson motorcycles.  Makes you want to go out and buy one.  So I did!

An extremely interesting documentary showing some amazing insights into motorcycle design and the practical problems surrounding the implementation of new concepts in design. It made me appreciate my Harley V Rod even more than I did before.
